details.sectionContent: This workshop is for the lover of aeronautics. You will be taught to build your own RC plane.
FIRST OF ALL WE WILL GIVE THE DIMENSION SHEET. THEN THEY HAVE TO PREPARE STRUCTURE OF RC PLANE. AFTER IT THE COMPONENT WILL BE PROVIDED TO THE PARTICIPANTS.
BATTERY, RECEIVER, MAIN ENGINE WILL BE ASSEMBLED FOR THE TESTING AND THE FLYING WILL BE CONDUCTED BY OUR RESPECTED SIR.

Location: Civil Seminar hall

  Session 2: @ 1:45 pm
